Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:04.71,Default,Fat,0000,0000,0000,,That's my swing, loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:08.67,Default,Haru,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:10.03,Default,Fat,0000,0000,0000,,What's it to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.03,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:57.01,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we could've moved the \Naudience more if we'd had the whole choir...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.55,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, about the choir club!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:02.99,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.24,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:09.21,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,The recital's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:10.55,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:11.90,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:15.40,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead and tell mom about my books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.74,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even have them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.60,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and my friends are all quitting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.22,Default,Mako,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to get real \Nmembers, on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:26.70,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to tell \Nyou how I found out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you stash your dirty books?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I asked mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:38.55,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 3\NSwinging and Meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.38,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a look at that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.81,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.07,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:40.29,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Do my eyes deceive me? \NCould this be... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:46.87,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your eyes and \Nhair match!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.93,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.80,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,You are so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.94,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,My lovely princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.34,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I am no money! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:00.91,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.55,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.52,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:20.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.65,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We're quitting the choir club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.49,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We got to see Kumagai Tetsuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.52,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.84,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the sheet music we borrowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.00,Default,paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Club Dissolution Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.00,Default,paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Choir Club
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.00,Default,paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Due to the reasons listed below, club \Nactivities are hereby terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.00,Default,paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}-Less than 5 members
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:39.00,Default,paper,0000,0000,0000,,Principal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.38,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow your clubs to continue
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without the minimum five members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:43.67,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.81,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,In short, your clubs have been dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:50.14,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But I have the prefectural \Ncompetition coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.49,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,All other clubs have found adequate members,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are staying within their limited budgets,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are complying with school regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.11,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.92,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Why does your group \Ndeserve special treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.53,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't, but the principal didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:08.52,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,The school regulations are written \Nin your student handbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While the principal remains hospitalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:16.29,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I am standing in for him as the \Nadministrator of this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.68,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Go wave your racket around in some park,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you want to play \Nbadminton by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.91,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,She actually said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:26.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Not with words, but it's what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.18,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Sure sounds like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.10,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,This is hopeless. Nothing will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.35,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't enter the competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.16,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:38.92,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I figured out that I can't have fake members,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll just have to find real ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.28,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.40,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.40,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We'll still have opportunities to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sing at the cultural \Nfestival or at graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.65,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you quit badminton \Nand join the choir club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:56.90,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.67,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you can't compete \Nin the prefecturals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your club's toast, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.57,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't given up on the competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm badminton's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:11.13,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.52,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, short stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the name-calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.53,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:17.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.41,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.49,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.14,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.65,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wien!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.43,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've got squirrels \Nin Japan as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.37,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:07.52,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.57,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play badminton?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:52.32,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've been recruited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:56.02,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, people don't usually go after seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.41,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Will I play in the competition too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.59,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.91,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I hope your application gets in on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:07.34,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I still need three more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.84,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it! Slam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.01,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever played badminton before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:13.89,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:18.18,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa had a badminton team at his work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he took me to see a few games.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:25.02,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I was really young, though, \Nso I don't remember much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.55,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, I forgot to lock up my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:31.94,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Go on in. My room's in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:32.71,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.76,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I'm borrowing the A/C.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.07,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Bouncy, bouncy, bunny hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:07.99,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I didn't think my \Nsister would be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:08.90,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:12.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tai-kun is so wrapped up in badminton,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he never brings friends over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:20.84,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am the one who is \Ntruly reprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.62,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Tai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.08,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.75,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.51,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sawa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:40.65,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Could I work at your beach house \Nagain this summer, Nagaoka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.46,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! You know we're \Nmore than happy to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will you still have time to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:50.61,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty. I have it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.60,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I look forward to summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me,too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:10:01.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting the strategy meeting for our summer \Nproject: "Ignite the Western Shopping District"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:57.91,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:02.83,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Sabure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.06,Default,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,Planning something like a cabaret...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:15.59,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and in summer, \Ncustomers are drawn to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:17.88,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the beach house will have it rough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.74,Default,Kawa,0000,0000,0000,,We need to attract men and women of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:26.37,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Western Shopping District Event Planning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:26.37,Default,Red,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's make this summer a hot one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:26.37,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Swimsuit Contest - Fireworks Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.00,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,What about a swimsuit competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:22.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Not again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.94,Default,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,That brings us right back \Nto where we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.94,0:10:26.39,Default,Shima,0000,0000,0000,,The beach is crowded enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.08,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What about music?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.48,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Music?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:37.37,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,It goes beyond male or \Nfemale, land or sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:45.95,Default,txt,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Cosplay Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.37,0:10:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since it's summer, \Nperformances could be held outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.40,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We could call it the \N"World Music Festival,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and turn the town into an international village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:56.80,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So if I win, you'll both \Njoin the badminton club?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:00.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You got it. But if {\i1}we{\i0} win,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to join our choir club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:03.72,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.52,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Can Tanaka even sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.58,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you said you needed real members.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.48,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Remember Ms. Takahashi's \Nfarewell party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.49,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right, he did sing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:23.42,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'd be useful, \Nif he put his mind to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.48,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but do you think he would?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:28.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! He seems easy to manipulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:31.71,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure Tanaka \Nwent to nationals last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.05,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Totally. It'll be three against one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.55,Default,Wak,0000,0000,0000,,Three against... I'm three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.02,Default,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I just need you for ten minutes at lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.77,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate sports?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:49.31,Default,Wak,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate them... But Okita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.98,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.62,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you really don't want to, \Nthe two of us will go,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.31,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,though you can always change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:10.85,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:11.87,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.27,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.64,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What were you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's three people in the choir club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.71,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi, you're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to tell me our practice schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.59,Default,Wak,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the badminton club?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.61,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me where to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.70,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have two people, since there \Nare two people in the badminton club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:37.19,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend you're playing for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.65,Default,Wak,0000,0000,0000,,If we do this, I want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:43.95,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.80,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to run into each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so a rule of thumb is \Nto stay in your area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:48.16,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.15,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We'll serve first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.15,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Best two out of three wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.30,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! All of you are serving at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:12:59.52,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.63,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:03.13,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.63,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,And, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:19.86,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wien!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.48,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I've got this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.85,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You see that, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.87,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,It's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.29,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Wakana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.29,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Sakai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.47,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Wa-Wakana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:40.46,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You were great, Sawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.07,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Sawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.72,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Archery does keep me fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.72,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretty close, \Nyourself, Miyamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:46.81,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.64,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:55.69,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've still lost, even without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.27,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:01.57,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.78,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Is your goal to be a professional singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.38,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't really thought that far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:12.79,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:17.21,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking I want \Nto continue badminton
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in college, and then go pro, if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.96,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Then aim for the world championships...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.78,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.81,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird to see him all timid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:30.38,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Lay off me, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.94,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,You'll go to the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:39.17,Default,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}New Club Application
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:39.17,Default,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Club Name: Choir and Sometimes Batminton Club
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:39.17,Default,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Name: Miyamoto Konatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:39.17,Default,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Club Activities: Singing, \Ndancing, occasionally batminton.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:39.19,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll need to put just \Nas much effort into the choir part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:40.74,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.78,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up! You planned this all along, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:52.32,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,But if we'd lost, it would've been the \N"Batminton and Sometimes Choir Club."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.73,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the choir group, too, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.42,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.20,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,In Japan, it's important to participate in both
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cultural {\i1}and{\i0} athletic clubs, \Nto cultivate cultural and martial excellence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.72,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Konatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.93,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Cultural and martial excellence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.41,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.46,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, it's "badminton", \Nnot "batminton."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.16,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.16,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked the principal if \Nhe would be our advisor again,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he told me to get everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.43,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any more supplementary \Nlessons until summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.67,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Those must be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.95,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound like you're not affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.06,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,The Choir and Sometimes Batminton Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.21,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's badminton.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:59.69,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't embarrass me too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.73,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.52,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,You know, our choir club used to be quite
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,famous for having won \Na national choir competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:15.62,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The choir club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.37,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Not the music club?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.26,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:21.58,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Sakai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.30,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.86,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,You do resemble her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.96,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother was one of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.60,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,She never told you about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:35.47,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:42.07,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting her changed the very \Nmeaning of music for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:47.01,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you could have \Ndescribed me as morendo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.48,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:56.65,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, there are some documents \Nhere I need you to review.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:58.45,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,This many?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:02.16,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Vice Principal, I'd like \Nyou to approve a new club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:09.22,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually think this \Nthing would get approved?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.59,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.55,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,You caused enough trouble at the last recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.76,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I will not stand to see \Nyou make a mockery of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.06,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.57,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,You will pick that up and throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.60,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I forgot to put my seal on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.10,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that darned thing go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.52,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you become their advisor again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.58,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,I might ask why you're so against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:09.02,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:12.76,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,When I think back on those times, \Nmy blood really gets pumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.76,0:18:14.91,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the same for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.88,Default,Prin,0000,0000,0000,,Or is the choir club already—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.19,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.75,Default,Vice,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please look \Nover those documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.69,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, napping in the \Nbeach house on the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,first day of summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.05,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.25,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,If we only have a regular daily practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to keep the members on their toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:51.80,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, practice starts at four today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:56.00,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are they building out front?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:59.78,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that? It's a stage for live music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.06,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,For that, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:11.48,Default,Poster,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Participate in our popularity \Ncontest and win shopping coupons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.30,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,The beach house and the \Nother businesses are
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going to each pick a country and build
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a small stage based on that theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.50,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Their singers will perform there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Shiho-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:15.02,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Large green tea snow cone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.13,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Comin' right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.49,Default,shi,0000,0000,0000,,Customers will vote on their favorites,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the winner will perform live on the \Nmain stage at the end of the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:29.85,Default,shi,0000,0000,0000,,Voters can even \Nwin shopping coupons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.40,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,How can you participate in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:39.75,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Each business is responsible \Nfor finding their own singers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.28,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,One large green tea snow cone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:45.41,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Would you let us sing for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:48.36,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, we have a prime location here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we were hoping to get someone \Nwho could really steal the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.58,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you let us audition?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.45,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,We might fit the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.30,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Please consider it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.29,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Summer Supplementary Class Schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.29,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mon|Tues|Wed|Thurs|Fri
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.29,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Eng.|Contemp. Lit.|World History|Jap. History|Politics & Econ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.29,Default,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Eng.|Classic Lit.|Eng. Classic Lit.|Contemp. Lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.94,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone must be at the beach house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:14.27,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.26,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.02,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:36.78,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I need to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.92,Default,Gai,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.53,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.09,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was at four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:49.56,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\a0} four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.18,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The competition's coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to waste \Ntime doing anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:56.22,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:58.57,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.67,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.47,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,The same as the recital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.34,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:07.98,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the school song?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.44,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:13.29,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:18.51,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to hear the voice \Nof the white beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:23.01,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so let's climb that winding slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.09,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:28.51,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The friendships we forge during \Nthese brilliant days and moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:27.15,Default,Naga,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sorry for the ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:32.67,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}create a harmony that stretches across eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.57,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Allegro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:36.75,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vivace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:40.54,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amorosso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.38,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's sing! Let's sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:48.69,Default,Song,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's sing, Shirahamazaka High!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:25.50,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:33.44,Default,Kona,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sing all by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.22,Default,Waka,0000,0000,0000,,Stalker! Stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.54,Default,Wien,0000,0000,0000,,Is that falsetto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:38.18,Default,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't Miyamoto coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:40.81,Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 4 \N Getting Angry and Dancing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.81,Default,Sawa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quitting the choir club! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
